**Rental of a 50ft Steel Walkway for the Canadian Coast Guard Vessel Vincent Massey**
====================================================================

**contractingEntityName**: Fisheries and Oceans Canada
**referenceNumber-numeroReference**: cb-364-56783164
**noticeURL-URLavis-eng**: [Available at the Canada Buys website](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/38620/30005753---rfp-gateway-rental-ccgs-vincent-massey.pdf)

### Details of the Tender Opportunity

The Canadian Coast Guard requires a rental of a 50ft steel walkway for the vessel Vincent Massey, newly upgraded for Canadian Coast Guard use. The existing bridges are not compatible with the new vessel, and therefore, need to be replaced.

### Specifications

* **Latitude/Longitude**: None
* **Region of Delivery**: Quebec (excluding National Capital Region)
* **Rental Period**: 
  * **Expected Start Date**: 2024-07-01
  * **Expected End Date**: 2025-03-31

### Solicitation Information

* **Solicitation Number**: 30005753
* **Request Type**: Request for Proposal
* **Form of Procurement**: Competitive

### Evaluation Criteria

Vendor proposals will be evaluated based on the **lowest price** submitted.

### Additional Details

* **Contact Information**: Louise Martel, 
  * E-mail: <DFO.tenders-soumissions.MPO@dfo-mpo.gc.ca>
  * Telephone: (819) 962-7325
* **Notice URL**: Not available.
* **Attachments**: Available at [Canada Buys Website](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/38620/30005753---rfp-gateway-rental-ccgs-vincent-massey.pdf)
